OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy rain through the
OL,8,Fevening and overnight. Increasingly
OL,9,Fdry and clear spells developing from
OL,10,Fthe west towards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry for many with bright
OL,13,Fspells but a few showers possible.
OL,14,FThese may be heavy at times.More
OL,15,Ffrequent showers spread into the west
OL,16,Fin the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
